description: If you’re craving a meal that leaves your gut, your wallet, and your passion for food bursting, you can find Chinese Laundry tumbling around the Arts District of downtown L.A., where they have mastered the art of serving incredibly flavorful Northern Chinese cuisine on the cheap.The once-starving artists of Los Angeles have rejoiced and continue to sing the praises of Chinese Laundry’s deliciously authentic noodle bowls and fantastically scrumptious pork belly tacos all over social media. Head on over, have your chopsticks at the ready, and help yourself to the daily specials that make everyday in L.A. special. Chinese Laundry is eager to hang with you.
name: Chinese Laundry
